high_descs: Turn left and look up at the cupboard.
Take a glass from the cupboard.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Put the glass inside to cool off then take it out.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Put the glass in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold glass in the microwave.

high_descs: Take a step  forward then turn left and walk to the counter.
Open the cupboard that's in front of you by your head and grab the cup that's up there then close the cupboard.
Turn left and walk to the fridge then turn right to face it.
Chill the cup in the freezer then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn left to face the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold cup in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter in front of the pan.
Open the upper cabinet and reach to take out the cup and then shut the door.
Go left and turn to face the fridge.
Put the cup in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick up the cup.
Go right and then turn to the left to face the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup in the microwave.
